data.description: Introducing 315 N Forrest Street in West York! This delightful brick cape cod, nestled within the West York Area School District, is ready for new owners. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, it's the ideal canvas for creating cherished memories. Situated on a generous 0.44-acre lot in the heart of West Manchester Township, this property provides ample outdoor space for your enjoyment. With 2,131 sqft of living area above grade and a partially finished basement, there's plenty of room to transform this house into your dream home. The added convenience of an attached 1-car garage is a practical bonus for your storage or parking needs. Don't let this opportunity to own a piece of York County pass you by. Contact us today to arrange a showing and start your journey to make this property your very own!
